| !Help for PipeDream
|
If "<File$Type_FAF>"="" Then Error No browser found to display HTML help
|
|If "<SparkFS$Dir>"="" Then Error SparkFS needs to be running to extract HTML help files
|RMEnsure SparkFS 1.42 Error SparkFS needs to be running to extract HTML help files
|
Set PipeDream$HelpFile <Obey$Dir>.Resource.HTMLHelp
IfThere <PipeDream$HelpFile> Then Else Set PipeDream$HelpFile <Obey$Dir>.^.HTMLHelp
IfThere <PipeDream$HelpFile> Then Filer_Run <PipeDream$HelpFile> Else Error PipeDream HTML help file not found
